metadata.name: Inside
metadata.description:
This spring is ambiguous for me, I work a lot on my inner world and it inspired me by many colors and meanings! But there are also many white spots and there is still a lot of work to be done on oneself.

I‘ve painted this artwork under the impression of my thoughts and feelings during kundalini yoga and meditation.

Acrylic on canvas
20x30 cm
Year: 2022

Svetlana Alekseenko
NFT: 2411 × 3759 px
